---
---
<section class="py-16 md:py-24 bg-[#0a0a0a] relative overflow-hidden px-4 sm:px-6">
  <div class="container mx-auto max-w-7xl">
    <h2 class="titulo-seccion mb-16 md:mb-20 text-center text-2xl md:text-3xl">Nuestros <span>Clientes</span></h2>
    
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8 sm:gap-10 md:gap-8 mt-8 md:mt-12">
      <!-- Testimonial 1 -->
      <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-[#1a1a1a] to-black p-6 sm:p-7 md:p-8 rounded-xl md:rounded-2xl border border-[var(--acento)]/20 shadow-[0_10px_30px_rgba(0,0,0,0.8)] relative transition-all duration-500 hover:border-[var(--acento)]/60 hover:-translate-y-2 group"><br><br><br>
        <div class="absolute -top-8 sm:-top-9 md:-top-10 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2">
          <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1500648767791-00dcc994a43e?q=80&w=200&auto=format&fit=crop" alt="Cliente" class="w-16 sm:w-18 md:w-20 h-16 sm:h-18 md:h-20 rounded-full border-4 border-black object-cover shadow-[0_0_15px_rgba(230,194,0,0.3)] group-hover:border-[var(--acento)] transition-colors duration-500">
        </div>
        <div class="flex justify-center mb-5 sm:mb-5 md:mb-6 mt-10 sm:mt-11 md:mt-6">
          <span class="text-[var(--acento)] text-lg sm:text-lg md:text-xl tracking-widest drop-shadow-[0_0_5px_rgba(230,194,0,0.5)]">★★★★★</span>
        </div>
        <p class="text-gray-300 italic text-center mb-5 sm:mb-5 md:mb-6 font-serif leading-relaxed text-sm sm:text-sm md:text-base line-clamp-none">"El mejor corte clásico que me han hecho en años. El ambiente es un verdadero lujo y el trato de primera. Mi lugar definitivo."</p>
        <h4 class="text-center font-bold text-white uppercase tracking-wider text-xs sm:text-xs md:text-sm font-sans">Alejandro M.</h4>
      </div>

      <!-- Testimonial 2 -->
      <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-[#1a1a1a] to-black p-6 sm:p-7 md:p-8 rounded-xl md:rounded-2xl border border-[var(--acento)]/40 shadow-[0_10px_40px_rgba(230,194,0,0.1)] relative transition-all duration-500 hover:border-[var(--acento)] hover:-translate-y-2 md:hover:-translate-y-10 group lg:md:-translate-y-8"><br><br><br>
        <div class="absolute -top-8 sm:-top-9 md:-top-10 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2">
          <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1506794778202-cad84cf45f1d?q=80&w=200&auto=format&fit=crop" alt="Cliente" class="w-16 sm:w-18 md:w-24 h-16 sm:h-18 md:h-24 rounded-full border-4 border-[var(--acento)] object-cover shadow-[0_0_20px_rgba(230,194,0,0.6)]">
        </div>
        <div class="flex justify-center mb-5 sm:mb-5 md:mb-6 mt-10 sm:mt-11 md:mt-8">
          <span class="text-[var(--acento)] text-lg sm:text-lg md:text-xl tracking-widest drop-shadow-[0_0_8px_rgba(230,194,0,0.8)]">★★★★★</span>
        </div>
        <p class="text-white italic text-center mb-5 sm:mb-5 md:mb-6 font-serif leading-relaxed text-sm sm:text-sm md:text-base md:text-lg line-clamp-none">"La atención al detalle en el perfilado de barba es impresionante. Te ofrecen un whisky mientras esperas. Una experiencia verdaderamente VIP."</p>
        <h4 class="text-center font-bold text-[var(--acento)] uppercase tracking-wider text-xs sm:text-xs md:text-sm font-sans">Roberto C.</h4>
      </div>

      <!-- Testimonial 3 -->
      <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-[#1a1a1a] to-black p-6 sm:p-7 md:p-8 rounded-xl md:rounded-2xl border border-[var(--acento)]/20 shadow-[0_10px_30px_rgba(0,0,0,0.8)] relative transition-all duration-500 hover:border-[var(--acento)]/60 hover:-translate-y-2 group md:col-span-2 lg:col-span-1"><br><br><br>
        <div class="absolute -top-8 sm:-top-9 md:-top-10 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2">
          <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1507003211169-0a1dd7228f2d?q=80&w=200&auto=format&fit=crop" alt="Cliente" class="w-16 sm:w-18 md:w-20 h-16 sm:h-18 md:h-20 rounded-full border-4 border-black object-cover shadow-[0_0_15px_rgba(230,194,0,0.3)] group-hover:border-[var(--acento)] transition-colors duration-500">
        </div>
        <div class="flex justify-center mb-5 sm:mb-5 md:mb-6 mt-10 sm:mt-11 md:mt-6">
          <span class="text-[var(--acento)] text-lg sm:text-lg md:text-xl tracking-widest drop-shadow-[0_0_5px_rgba(230,194,0,0.5)]">★★★★★</span>
        </div>
        <p class="text-gray-300 italic text-center mb-5 sm:mb-5 md:mb-6 font-serif leading-relaxed text-sm sm:text-sm md:text-base line-clamp-none">"Profesionalismo puro. Llevo a mi hijo de 10 años y le tienen una paciencia increíble. El resultado siempre es impecable."</p>
        <h4 class="text-center font-bold text-white uppercase tracking-wider text-xs sm:text-xs md:text-sm font-sans">David S.</h4>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .titulo-seccion {
      font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 5vw, 2rem);
    }
    .grid {
      gap: 1.5rem !important;
    }
  }
  
  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .grid {
      gap: 2rem !important;
    }
  }
</style>
